race.description: The Q - Engineered By Stp Consultants
race.comment: BOGIE BECKER (1) has mixed form a little and missed the frame the last two but was a Maiden winner three back (19.27) at this track over 350m. Likely to improve sharply this time. FAME BECKONS (3) doesn't have the best strike-rate. Finished in the minors latest when third (22.29) at Q Lakeside and may be close to breaking through. Leading player again. DAZZLING LIZZIE (4) is having her first start around this circuit. Comes here after a last start 4th and beaten 12 lengths (20.28) at Q Lakeside. Bold showing expected. IT'S MY CASH (2) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.
